a]]'' (1996)\n|-\n| ''[[Maurice (novel)|Maurice]]'' (1971), [[E. M. Forster]]\n| ''[[Maurice (film)|Maurice]]'' (1987)\n|-\n| ''[[The Mayor of Casterbridge]]'' (1886), [[Thomas Hardy]]\n| ''[[The Mayor of Casterbridge (1921 film)|The Mayor of Casterbridge]]'' (1921)<br />''[[The Mayor of Casterbridge#Adaptations - A 1978 television film by Dennis Potter for the BBC starring Alan Bates as Henchard, Anna Massey as Lucetta, and Anne Stallybrass as Susan.|The Mayor of Casterbridge]]'' (1978) (TV)<br />''[[The Mayor of Casterbridge#Adaptations - In 2001 (broadcast on ITV 2003) by Georgina Lowe, with Ciar\u00e1n Hinds as Henchard, Polly Walker as Lucetta, James Purefoy as Farfrae and Jodhi May as Elizabeth Jane.|The Mayor of Casterbridge]]'' (2003) (TV)<br />''[[The Claim (2000 film)|The Claim]]'' (2000)\n|-\n| ''[[McTeague]]'' (1899), [[Frank Norris]]\n| ''[[McTeague (film)|McTeague]]'' (1916)<br />''[[Greed (1924 film)|Greed]]'' (1924)\n|-\n|''[[Me and Earl and the Dying Girl]]'' (2012), [[Jesse Andrews]]\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Me and Earl and the Dying Girl (2015)|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2582496/?ref_=nv_sr_1|accessdate=2017-08-04}}</ref>[[Me and Earl and the Dying Girl (film)|''Me and Earl and the Dying Girl'']] (2015)\n|-\n| ''[[The Medusa Touch]]'' (1973), [[Peter Van Greenaway]]\n| ''[[The Medusa Touch (film)|The Medusa Touch]]'' (1978)\n|-\n| ''[[The Memoirs of Cleopatra]]'' (1997), [[Margaret George]]\n| ''[[Cleopatra (1999 film)|Cleopatra]]'' (1999)\n|-\n| ''The Mephisto Waltz'' (1969), [[Fred Mustard Stewart]]\n| ''[[The Mephisto Waltz]]'' (1971)\n|-\n| ''Mercy Island'' (1941), [[Theodore Pratt]]\n| ''[[Mercy Island]]'' (1941)\n|-\n| ''[[Merton of the Movies (novel)|Merton of the Movies]]'' (1919), [[Harry Leon Wilson]]\n| ''[[Merton of the Movies (1924 film)|Merton of the Movies]]'' (1924)<br />''[[Make Me a Star (film)|Make Me a Star]]'' (1932)<br />''[[Merton of the Movies (1947 film)|Merton of the Movies]]'' (1947)\n|-\n| ''[[Message in a Bottle (