evision - The Bishop's Candlesticks (1929)|The Bishop's Candlesticks]]'' (1929)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Aa Mujou (1929)|Aa Mujou]]'' (1929)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Jean Valjean (1931)|Jean Valjean]]'' (1931)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Les Mis\u00e9rables (1934 film)|Les Mis\u00e9rables]]'' (1934)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Les Mis\u00e9rables (1935 film)|Les Mis\u00e9rables]]'' (1935)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Gavrosh (1937)|Gavrosh]]'' (1937)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Kyojindern (1938)|Kyojinden]]'' (1938)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Los Miserables (1943 film)|Los Miserables]]'' (1943)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - El Boassa (1944)|El Boassa]]'' (1944)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Les Mis\u00e9rables (1948 film)|I Miserabili]]'' (1948)<small>(Re-released in 1952)</small><br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Les Nouveaux Mis\u00e9rables (1949)|Les Nouveaux Mis\u00e9rables]]'' (1949)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Re mizeraburu: Kami to Akuma (Les Mis\u00e9rables: Gods and Demons) (1950)|Re mizeraburu: Kami to Akuma]]'' (''Les Mis\u00e9rables: Gods and Demons'') (1950)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Ezhai Padum Padu (1950)|Ezhai Padum Padu]]'' (1950)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Beedala Patlu (1950)|Beedala Patlu]]'' (1950)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables (1952 film)|Les Mis\u00e9rables]]'' (1952)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Kundan (1955)|Kundan]]'' (1955)<br />''[[Les Mis\u00e9rables#Adaptations - Film and television - Duppathage Duka (1956)|Duppathage Duka]]'' (195