 Turning'') (1939)<br />''[[Ossessione]]'' (''Obsession'') (1942)<br />''[[The Postman Always Rings Twice (1946 film)|The Postman Always Rings Twice]]'' (1946)<br />''[[The Postman Always Rings Twice (1981 film)|The Postman Always Rings Twice]]'' (1981)\n|-\n| ''[[The Power (1956 novel)|The Power]]'' (1956), [[Frank M. Robinson]]\n| ''[[The Power (1968 film)|The Power]]'' (1968)\n|-\n| ''[[The Power and the Glory]]'' (1940), [[Graham Greene]]\n| ''[[The Fugitive (1947 film)|The Fugitive]]'' (1947)\n|-\n| ''[[The Power of One (novel)|The Power of One]]'' (1989), [[Bryce Courtenay]]\n| ''[[The Power of One (film)|The Power of One]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| ''Po\u017cegnania'' (1948), [[Stanis\u0142aw Dygat]]\n| ''[[Farewells]]'' (1958)\n|-\n| ''[[Presumed Innocent (novel)|Presumed Innocent]]'' (1987), [[Scott Turow]]\n| ''[[Presumed Innocent (film)|Presumed Innocent]]'' (1990)\n|-\n| ''[[Pride and Prejudice]]'' (1813), [[Jane Austen]]\n| ''[[Pride and Prejudice (1940 film)|Pride and Prejudice]]'' (1940)<br />''[[Pride & Prejudice: A Latter-Day Comedy]]'' (2003)<br />''[[Bride and Prejudice]]'' (2004)<br />''[[Pride & Prejudice (2005 film)|Pride & Prejudice]]'' (2005)\n|-\n| ''[[The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1881), [[Mark Twain]]\n| ''[[The Prince and the Pauper (film)#The Prince and the Pauper (1909 film)|The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1909)<br />''[[The Prince and the Pauper (film)#The Prince and the Pauper (1915 film)|The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1915)<br />''[[The Prince and the Pauper#Film, TV, theatrical and other adaptations - Der Prinz und der Bettelknabe (1920 film)|Der Prinz und der Bettelknabe]]'' (1920)<br />''[[Yiskor]]'' (1933)<br />''[[The Prince and the Pauper (1937 film)|The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1937)<br />''[[The Prince and the Pauper (film)#The Prince and the Pauper (1943 film)|The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1943)<br />''[[The Prince and the Pauper (film)#The Prince and the Pauper (1962 film)|The Prince and the Pauper]]'' (1962)<br />''[[Raja Aur Run