unro Oshikawa]]<br />''Kaitei Okoku'' (1931), Shigeru Komatsuzaki\n| ''[[Atragon]]'' (1963)<br />''[[Atragon#Super Atragon|Super Atragon]]'' (1995)\n|-\n| ''Kami no Tsuki'' (2012), [[Mitsuyo Kakuta]]\n| ''[[Pale Moon (film)|Pale Moon]]'' (2014)\n|-\n| ''Kenka erejii'' (1963), Takashi Suzuki\n| ''[[Fighting Elegy]]'' (1966)\n|-\n| ''[[The Keys of the Kingdom]]'' (1941), [[A. J. Cronin]]\n| ''[[The Keys of the Kingdom (film)|The Keys of the Kingdom]]'' (1944)\n|-\n| ''Khamphiphaksa'' (''The Judgment'') (1981), [[Chart Korbjitti]]\n| ''[[Ai-Fak]]'' (2004)\n|-\n| ''[[Kidnapped (novel)|Kidnapped]]'' (1886), [[Robert Louis Stevenson]]\n| ''[[Kidnapped (1938 film)|Kidnapped]]'' (1938)<br />''[[Kidnapped (1960 film)|Kidnapped]]'' (1960)<br />''[[Kidnapped (1971 film)|Kidnapped]]'' (1971)<br />''[[Kidnapped (1995 film)|Kidnapped]]'' (1995)\n|-\n| ''[[The King's Damosel]]'' (1976), [[Vera Chapman]]\n| ''[[Quest for Camelot]]'' (1998)\n|-\n| ''Kings Row'' (1940), [[Henry Bellamann]]\n| ''[[Kings Row]]'' (1942), directed by Sam Wood\n|-\n| ''[[King Solomon's Mines]]'' (1885), Sir [[H. Rider Haggard]]\n| ''[[King Solomon's Mines (film)#Allan Quatermain (1919 film)|Allan Quatermain]]'' (1919)<br />''[[King Solomon's Mines (1937 film)|King Solomon's Mines]]'' (1937)<br />''[[King Solomon's Mines (1950 film)|King Solomon's Mines]]'' (1950)<br />* ''[[Watusi (film)|Watusi]]'' (1959)<br />''[[King Solomon's Mines (film)#King Solomon's Treasure (1977)|King Solomon's Treasure]]'' (1977)<br />''[[King Solomon's Mines (1985 film)|King Solomon's Mines]]'' (1985)<br />* ''[[Allan Quatermain and the Lost City of Gold]]'' (1987)<br />''[[King Solomon's Mines (film)#King Solomon's Mines (1986 film)|King Solomon's Mines]]'' (1986)<br />''[[The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen (film)|The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen]]'' (2003)<br />''[[King Solomon's Mines (2004 film)|King Solomon's Mines]]'' (2004) (TV) (mini)<br />''[[Allan Quatermain and the Temple of Skulls]]'' (2008)\n|-\n| ''King's 