pei'', ''Les Derniers Jours de Pomp\u00e9i'') (1950)<br />''[[The Last Days of Pompeii#Film, TV and theatrical adaptations - The Last Days of Pompeii (1959 film)|The Last Days of Pompeii]]'' (''Gli ultimi giorni di Pompei'') (1959)\n|-\n| ''The Last Detail'' (1970), [[Darryl Ponicsan]]\n| ''[[The Last Detail]]'' (1973)\n|-\n| ''[[The Last Hunt (western novel)|The Last Hunt]]'' (1954), [[Milton Lott]]\n| ''[[The Last Hunt]]'' (1956)\n|-\n| ''[[Last of the Duanes (novel)|The Last of the Duanes]]'' (1913) (written), (1996) (published), [[Zane Grey]]\n| ''[[The Last of the Duanes (1919 film)|The Last of the Duanes]]'' (1919)<br />''[[The Last of the Duanes (1924 film)|The Last of the Duanes]]'' (1924)<br />''[[The Last of the Duanes (1930 film)|The Last of the Duanes]]'' (1930)<br />''[[El \u00faltimo de los Vargas]]'' (1930)<br />''[[Last of the Duanes (1941 film)|Last of the Duanes]]'' (1941)\n|-\n| ''[[The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1826), [[James Fenimore Cooper]]\n| ''[[The Last of the Mohicans#Films - The Last of the Mohicans (1912 film)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1912)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans (1920 American film)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1920) (made in America)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans (1920 German film)|Der Letzte der Mohikaner]]'' (''The Last of the Mohicans'') (1920) (made in Germany)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans (1932 serial)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1932) (serial)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans (1936 film)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1936)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans (1971 series)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1971) (TV) (serial)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans#TV - The Last of the Mohicans (1977 television film)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1977) (TV)<br />''[[The Last of the Mohicans (1992 film)|The Last of the Mohicans]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| ''The Last Picture Show'' (1966), [[Larry McMurtry]]\n| ''[[The Last Picture Show]]'' (1971)\n|-\n| ''[[The Last Ride (novel)|The Last Ride]]'' (1996), [[Thomas Eidson]]\n|