on]]\n| ''[[The Other Side of Midnight (film)|The Other Side of Midnight]]'' (1977)\n|-\n| ''Our Girl Friday'' (1951), [[Ernest K. Gann]]\n| ''[[Our Girl Friday]]'' (1953) (a. k. a. ''The Adventures of Sadie'')\n|-\n| ''[[Our Man in Havana]]'' (1958), [[Graham Greene]]\n| ''[[Our Man in Havana (film)|Our Man in Havana]]'' (1959)\n|-\n| ''Out of Sight'' (1996), [[Elmore Leonard]]\n| ''[[Out of Sight]]'' (1998)\n|-\n| ''[[An Outcast of the Islands]]'' (1896), [[Joseph Conrad]]\n| ''[[An Outcast of the Islands#Film adaptation - An Outcast of the Islands (1952 film)|An Outcast of the Islands]]'' (1952)\n|-\n| ''[[The Outsiders (novel)|The Outsiders]]'' (1967), [[S. E. Hinton]]\n| ''[[The Outsiders (film)|The Outsiders]]'' (1983)\n|-\n| ''Over the River'' (1933), [[John Galsworthy]]\n| ''[[One More River]]'' (1934)\n|-\n| ''[[The Ox-Bow Incident (novel)|The Ox-Bow Incident]]'' (1940), [[Walter Van Tilburg Clark]]\n| ''[[The Ox-Bow Incident]]'' (1943)\n|}\n\n=== P ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=\"800\"|Fiction work(s) !! width=\"800\"|Film adaptation(s)\n|-\n| ''A Painted Devil'' (1966), Thomas P. Cullinan\n| ''[[The Beguiled (1971 film)|The Beguiled]]'' (1971)\n|-\n| ''[[A Painted House]]'' (2001), [[John Grisham]]\n| ''[[A Painted House#Television adaptation|A Painted House]]'' (2003) (TV)\n|-\n| ''[[The Painted Veil (novel)|The Painted Veil]]'' (1925), [[W. Somerset Maugham]]\n| ''[[The Painted Veil (1934 film)|The Painted Veil]]'' (1934)<br />''[[The Seventh Sin]]'' (1957)<br />''[[The Painted Veil (2006 film)|The Painted Veil]]'' (2006)\n|-\n| ''[[Pan Wolodyjowski]]'' (''Fire in the Steppe'') (1888), [[Henryk Sienkiewicz]]\n| ''[[Colonel Wolodyjowski (film)|Colonel Wolodyjowski]]'' (1968)\n|-\n| ''[[Parineeta (novel)|Parineeta]]'' (1914), [[Sharat Chandra Chattopadhyay]]\n| ''[[Parineeta (1942 film)|Parineeta]]'' (1942)<br />''[[Parineeta (1953 film)|Parineeta]]'' (1953)<br />''[[Parineeta (1969 film)|Parineeta]]'' (1969)<br />''[[Parineeta (2005 film)|Pari